[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=6][B]English[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=5][B]Announcement[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
Hello Shotbow!
 
It's my honor to be giving you this news today: news that has been long awaited by our entire staff team for the past few months.
 
As you may know, in recent times Shotbow has been experiencing intermittent downtime and connection instability due to persistent, daily ongoing DDoS attacks. We recently [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/state-of-shotbow.394339/']released a statement[/URL] of our game plan, and we're happy to be announcing a status update today.
 
Since the attacks started, we were in touch with our host in order to set up a mitigation service, but unfortunately with little success.
 
In the past few weeks, however, we set up a new DDoS mitigation service with [URL='https://path.net/']Path[/URL]. Path's service works as a firewall against these large DDoS attacks, while still routing all normal player traffic directly to our same old host.
 
We have been testing the pathway for the last few days, and we're happy to announce that we have mitigated all DDoS attacks that have come our way, allowing for a steady and uninterrupted connection to Shotbow for all.
 
As an added bonus, the Path also specializes in internet routing, which means that you will probably noticed improved latencies when connecting to Shotbow. Please let us know how your ping has changed in the comments!
 
[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=5][B]Celebration[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
Team morale behind-the-scenes has been down for the past few months as the constant deluge of attacks has diverted our attention from code and builds to dealing with DDoS attacks. Now that we're past this hurdle, it's time to celebrate! Here's some reasons to get back on the server this weekend:
[LIST]
[*]A 33% sale on [COLOR=#c0c0c0][B]Silver[/B][/COLOR], [COLOR=#ffcc00][B]Gold[/B][/COLOR], and [COLOR=#00ffff][B]Platinum[/B][/COLOR] in our [URL='https://minez.buycraft.net/']Shotbow Shop[/URL]!
[*]A (very generous) [B][COLOR=#00ff00]+10x XP multiplier[/COLOR][/B] this Saturday and Sunday
[/LIST]
These offers will start on Saturday and will go until Sunday night. As you know, during the DDoS attacks, our playercount has dwindled, so we hope these incentives will help you get back into the Shotbow that you've always known and loved.
 
[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=5][B]Closing Words[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
All of us on the Shotbow team are just as excited as you are to see Shotbow back and stronger than ever. Our improved connection and DDoS mitigation will allow the staff to focus on delivering new and improved content to you as often as we possiby can, and we hope that this was a step in the right direction. As always, thanks for flying Shotbow. Now, please enjoy our monthly newsletter below!
 
